Trinity College in Dublin. And this afternoon, I'm going to discuss a

73
00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:23.600
pan-cancer analysis of rare RAS alleles using

74
00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:26.620
AACR Project Genie. I'm going to focus on their prevalence,

