713
00:41:34.464 --> 00:41:37.844
This is our baseline characteristics of our cohort

714
00:41:38.104 --> 00:41:40.944
across 143,000 patients.

715
00:41:42.364 --> 00:41:46.204
We saw a prevalence of KMT2C mutation of 5.2%.

716
00:41:47.144 --> 00:41:51.104
The distribution of age, sex, and race were

717
00:41:51.184 --> 00:41:54.884
