926
00:53:48.510 --> 00:53:48.850
and

927
00:53:52.030 --> 00:53:55.150
resulting in enhanced downstream ARC signaling.

928
00:53:56.510 --> 00:54:00.330
This paradoxical activation is key why class two

929
00:54:00.550 --> 00:54:03.010
fundamentally require different

930
00:54:04.550 --> 00:54:05.770
