1217
01:11:34.926 --> 01:11:38.686
So in conclusion, Ultima Genomics PPMseq assay provides a

1218
01:11:38.726 --> 01:11:42.546
highly sensitive, cost-efficient, and also adaptable whole

1219
01:11:42.606 --> 01:11:45.306
genome sequencing assay for cell-free DNA.

1220
01:11:45.986 --> 01:11:49.386
We can monitor tumor mutational burden and large clones in these processes.

1221
01:11:49.426 --> 01:11:52.926
And also we can identify a greater variety of resistance

1222
01:11:53.006 --> 01:11:56.086
mechanisms in response to treatment using whole genome sequencing, including

1223
01:11:56.146 --> 01:11:59.606
structural variants, copy number changes, the non-coding drivers, all of which

1224
01:11:59.626 --> 01:12:03.206
we're collecting more and more information about how they're really essential

1225
01:12:03.266 --> 01:12:06.966
to cancer and development. And also whole genome tissue and whole genome

1226
01:12:07.566 --> 01:12:11.246
sequencing cell-free DNA can provide the most comprehensive picture of a cancer

